#- The following lines are examples of what might be required to use NFS,
#- rather than FTP, for booting the VME crate, and generally for reading
#- and writing files on the server.

#- Needed for nfs v3+, set the UID and GID the VME will use 
nfsAuthUnixSet("s100dserv", <uid>, <gid>, 0, 0)

#- Register the IP addresses for the hosts of any mounts
hostAdd("s100data","<ip_data>")
hostAdd("s100dserv", "<ip_dserv>")

#- Mount what you need
nfsMount("s100dserv","/APSshare","/APSshare")
nfsMount("s100data","/xorApps","/net/s100data/xorApps")
